MENU
Descriptive Statistics
1. Grouped Data
2. Ungrouped Data
3. Quit

***GROUPED DATA***

-asks for input
1. integer only
2. floating point only

-enter total number of items
-check for validation

-displays [indexed] data with heading [description] - prompt the user for description 

-asks if user wishes to edit data


loop until user chooses continue{
1. Continue
2. Edit
  if edit, proceed to edit
  
  else (user chose Continue) 
    display accordingly [radio button]
    1. Mean
    2. Median
    3. Mode
      1. unimodal
      2. bimodal
      3. multimodal
      4. no modal class
      
    4. all
}

